         \ufeff\ny\u22650\ny\u22650\ufeff \n\n\n\n\nStaring at the above for long enough, we see the following chain of (in)equalites fall out:\n\n\n\n\n\ufeff\ncTx=xTc\u2264xTATy=(Ax)Ty\u2264bTy\nc\nT\nx=x\nT\nc\u2264x\nT\nA\nT\ny=(Ax)\nT\ny\u2264b\nT\ny\ufeff \n\n\n\n\nIn particular, we get \ufeff\ncTx\u2264bTy\nc\nT\nx\u2264b\nT\ny\ufeff , or weak duality!\n\n\n", "updatedAt": 1714669231222}